mpdmacs News -- history of user-visible changes           -*- outline -*-

* mpdmacs 1.0

** 1.0.1

No user-visible changes-- hygienic release only.
** 1.0.0

*** User-visible changes

**** Introduce a Texinfo user manual.
*** Bugfixes

**** Introduce `mpdmacs-current-song-line-face'

This will remove an inadvertent dependency on `all-the-icons'.
* 0.4 builds

** 0.4.1

No user-visible changes; this was strictly a hygienic release.
** 0.4.0

*** User-visible changes

**** Introduced two new functions `mpdmacs-connection-status' & `mpdmacs-connection-failed-p'
* 0.3 builds

** 0.3.0

*** User-visible changes

**** `mpdmacs-show-current-song` now lists playlists in which the song is included
* 0.2 builds
** 0.2.2

*** User-visible changes

**** Minor fontifying of the current-song buffer
** 0.2.1

Incorporated more lints from MELPA submission.
** 0.2.0

*** User-visible changes

Now exposed as a minor mode.
* 0.1 builds

** 0.1.5

Incorporated lints from MELPA submission.
** 0.1.4

Final touch-up before pushing to Github (docs only).
** 0.1.3

*** User-visible changes

  - Adds 'mpdmacs-sticker-change-hook'
  - Adds 'mpdmacs-show-current-song-hook'
  - Added 'mpdmacs-set-crossfade'
  - Added 'mpdmacs-rotate-single'
  - Added 'mpdmacs-rotate-replay-gain'
  - Added 'mdpmacs-show-current-song'
  - Makes 'mpdmacs-unload' idempotent
*** Bugfixes

  - Fixed a bug in 'mpdmacs-send-to-playlist'
  - Fixed a bug in 'mpdmacs-dec-volume'
** 0.1.2

Numerous breaking changes.
** 0.1.1

Numerous breaking changes.
** 0.1.0

Initial commit of `mpdmacs'!

